product_info.title: Leather Little Lifter
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesThe original bicycle frame handle launched by Walnut Studiolo on Kickstarter. The frame handle (a.k.a. “The Little Lifter”!) is a comfortable, stylish, sturdy, and easy-to-use leather handle for carrying your bicycle, whether it's up the stairs, across the tracks, or onto the metro. Designed for commuters, this minimalist handle makes carrying your bike actually feel easier and lighter by lowering the center of gravity and using your normal muscle groups for lifting and holding your bicycle, same as lifting a grocery bag or carrying a briefcase. Most riders pick up their bike by the top tube, which requires you to bend your elbow at an uncomfortable angle. This causes strain on your elbow and shoulder and makes carrying your bike any distance feel awkward. Because it’s easier to lift a bike with the Frame Handle, you’re more in control when walking up stairs or in a crowded setting. The Frame Handle has two adjustable buckles. One that wraps around the down-tube and one around the seat-tube. It can be mounted above the derailleur and below most water bottle cages. The leather used is USA-tanned leather from American steers in St. Louis, Missouri with hardware sourced from an Ohio leather company.

product_info.title: Red Wing Iron Ranger Boot

The Mesabi Iron Range lies in northern Minnesota, a rugged and remote area known for its iron mines. The local residents who work these mines are proudly known as Iron Rangers, individuals with a sense of adventure and a determined personality. Originally designed to be worn in the iron mines, Iron Ranger work boots had to be as tough as the people who wore them in demanding conditions. product_info.title: Shiny Object CO2 Inflator
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesCarrying a pump everywhere can be a drag. Getting a flat tire while you're out is even worse! You know what's not awful? The Portland Design Works Shiny Object CO2 inflator. With this bad boy, you can leave the pump at home and, if you get a flat, you're just a twist of the cartridge away from rolling again! Plus, the Shiny Object has a built-in valve so you can pop a cartridge on there and not have to worry about accidentally emptying your CO2 (say, "goodbye" to premature evacuation)! Did I mention that it works with presta and schrader valves? Well it does, and that means, no matter what you're riding, popping the Shiny Object in your pocket before you head out could be the difference between riding and walking home! It even comes with a CO2 cartridge, a classy leather sleeve, and it'll take any 16g threaded CO2 cartridges you can find, so grab one and get riding! Your friends will totally be jealous of how shiny it is. PDF Instructions

product_info.title: Knog Blinder Road Rear Light
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesNow for the tale of the Knog Blinder Road Rear. This rear light has a colossal 70 lumen strobe, with numerous settings for every riding situation. target_product.title: Red Wing Iron Ranger Boot
target_product.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from United By Blue. The Mesabi Iron Range lies in northern Minnesota, a rugged and remote area known for its iron mines. The local residents who work these mines are proudly known as Iron Rangers, individuals with a sense of adventure and a determined personality. Originally designed to be worn in the iron mines, Iron Ranger work boots had to be as tough as the people who wore them in demanding conditions. Iron Ranger boots are built with a double layer of leaver over the toe to provide an extra measure of safety. 6 inch, Amber Harness leather with Nitrile Cork sole.

product_info.title: Reynolds 66mm Carbon Tubular Pro Wheel
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesReynolds 66mm Carbon Tubular Pro Wheel Excuses are cheap. Losing another race, being late for another date, getting chumped again by the grandma on the mountain bike; they're not the end of the world - and they're a heck of a lot cheaper than these wheels. But maybe that's not good enough for you. Maybe you've gone as far as you want to go on excuses and now you want to see how you'll do with nothing standing in your way. These tubeless Reynolds wheels weigh a combined 3lbs 13oz, are made from race-ready carbon fiber, and are buttery smooth. They're not guaranteed to make you win, but they're guaranteed to prevent any post-race blame-game-ing about your equipment not being up to the task. Heads up though, there's a lot of pressure when the weakest part of your bike is you; are you ready for that?

product_info.title: Nantucket Cruiser Pannier Basket
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesThe family that owns and runs Nantucket Bike Baskets has been in the basket-making industry for over 30 years, and it shows. Not satisfied with only basketing-out the front of the bike, they've started weaving these amazing basket panniers that hook directly to your rear rack! Pop it off and take it into the store while you grab your groceries, pop it back on your rack when you're done shopping and cruise home! Woven using the highest quality rattan which weathers nicely over time for an antique look, this isn't your average department store-basket, it's a practical work of art that'll help you and your bike thrive in your city!

product_info.title: Shiny Object CO2 Inflator
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesCarrying a pump everywhere can be a drag. Getting a flat tire while you're out is even worse! You know what's not awful? The Portland Design Works Shiny Object CO2 inflator. With this bad boy, you can leave the pump at home and, if you get a flat, you're just a twist of the cartridge away from rolling again! Plus, the Shiny Object has a built-in valve so you can pop a cartridge on there and not have to worry about accidentally emptying your CO2 (say, "goodbye" to premature evacuation)! Did I mention that it works with presta and schrader valves? Well it does, and that means, no matter what you're riding, popping the Shiny Object in your pocket before you head out could be the difference between riding and walking home! It even comes with a CO2 cartridge, a classy leather sleeve, and it'll take any 16g threaded CO2 cartridges you can find, so grab one and get riding! Your friends will totally be jealous of how shiny it is. PDF Instructions

product_info.title: Leather Little Lifter
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesThe original bicycle frame handle launched by Walnut Studiolo on Kickstarter. The frame handle (a.k.a. “The Little Lifter”!) is a comfortable, stylish, sturdy, and easy-to-use leather handle for carrying your bicycle, whether it's up the stairs, across the tracks, or onto the metro. Designed for commuters, this minimalist handle makes carrying your bike actually feel easier and lighter by lowering the center of gravity and using your normal muscle groups for lifting and holding your bicycle, same as lifting a grocery bag or carrying a briefcase. Most riders pick up their bike by the top tube, which requires you to bend your elbow at an uncomfortable angle. This causes strain on your elbow and shoulder and makes carrying your bike any distance feel awkward. Because it’s easier to lift a bike with the Frame Handle, you’re more in control when walking up stairs or in a crowded setting. The Frame Handle has two adjustable buckles. One that wraps around the down-tube and one around the seat-tube. It can be mounted above the derailleur and below most water bottle cages. The leather used is USA-tanned leather from American steers in St. Louis, Missouri with hardware sourced from an Ohio leather company.

product_info.title: Shiny Object CO2 Inflator
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesCarrying a pump everywhere can be a drag. Getting a flat tire while you're out is even worse! You know what's not awful? The Portland Design Works Shiny Object CO2 inflator. With this bad boy, you can leave the pump at home and, if you get a flat, you're just a twist of the cartridge away from rolling again! Plus, the Shiny Object has a built-in valve so you can pop a cartridge on there and not have to worry about accidentally emptying your CO2 (say, "goodbye" to premature evacuation)! Did I mention that it works with presta and schrader valves? Well it does, and that means, no matter what you're riding, popping the Shiny Object in your pocket before you head out could be the difference between riding and walking home! It even comes with a CO2 cartridge, a classy leather sleeve, and it'll take any 16g threaded CO2 cartridges you can find, so grab one and get riding! Your friends will totally be jealous of how shiny it is. PDF Instructions

product_info.title: Knog Blinder Road Rear Light
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesNow for the tale of the Knog Blinder Road Rear. This rear light has a colossal 70 lumen strobe, with numerous settings for every riding situation. With the Knog’s blindingly bright beam, it will be as if you are standing atop Mount Olympus, shouting with the thunder of a thousand sirens. “See me,” you will scream, “FEAR ME!” And all will see you and watch with awe and pure wonder as you ride to battle your foes. Truly, this is the light of heroes. So grab one, and be epic! Specs 70 lumens in strobe mode (peak) Dimensions: W27mm x H76mm x D52mm Weight: 52g Materials: UV-Resistant, industrial-grade Silicone Rubber Body and Straps. Polycarbonate Housing. PMMA Lens. Anodised Aluminium Heat sink. Anodised Aluminium Fascia and solid Stainless Steel MIMLatch. Rechargeable Lithium Polymer (USB). This saves using about 600 AAA Alkaline batteries during the lights lifetime. Features LEDs: 1 x CREE XPD XB-D LED, 3 x Super bright LEDs Lens: Collimated optics. Visibility: Visible from a distance of min. 1000 metres. Incorporates side Illumination with visibility of 290° Beam Angle (degrees): Wide beam 80°. Narrow beam 22° LiPo Technology with battery protection circuit. USB Rechargeable and extension cord included. Constant current drive technology: Maintains consistent brightness throughout specified run-time. Integrated USB Plug: Designed to be exposed to the elements, the plug is also waterproof and will not be damaged by exposure. Waterproof: 100% Waterproof and Dust Proof. Light Modes: 5 light modes: 1.Steady, 2.Fast, 3.Chaser, 4.Peleton, 5. Eco-Flash. Burn time: lasting up to 3.5 hours in Steady mode, 4 hours in Fast, 5 hours in Chaser, 13 hours in Peloton Mode and 20 hours in Eco-Flash. Charge time: 5 hour charge time Button: New longer button push on (0.75sec) prevents accidental activation of your light. Shortpresses switch modes continuously. Similarly, the light is switched off with a long button push off (0.5sec). Low battery indicator Bike Attachment: Tool-less attachment for standard rear posts measuring 22-32mm. Not suitable for aero post design Testing: The Blinder Road has been tested against the following; Drop tests, corrosion tests, UV tests,Electrical shock and static, vibration and impact, temperature and humidity, cycle testing and CE certification.

product_info.title: Red Wing Iron Ranger Boot
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from United By Blue. The Mesabi Iron Range lies in northern Minnesota, a rugged and remote area known for its iron mines. The local residents who work these mines are proudly known as Iron Rangers, individuals with a sense of adventure and a determined personality. Originally designed to be worn in the iron mines, Iron Ranger work boots had to be as tough as the people who wore them in demanding conditions. Iron Ranger boots are built with a double layer of leaver over the toe to provide an extra measure of safety. 6 inch, Amber Harness leather with Nitrile Cork sole.

product_info.title: Reynolds 66mm Carbon Tubular Pro Wheel
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesReynolds 66mm Carbon Tubular Pro Wheel Excuses are cheap. Losing another race, being late for another date, getting chumped again by the grandma on the mountain bike; they're not the end of the world - and they're a heck of a lot cheaper than these wheels. But maybe that's not good enough for you. Maybe you've gone as far as you want to go on excuses and now you want to see how you'll do with nothing standing in your way. These tubeless Reynolds wheels weigh a combined 3lbs 13oz, are made from race-ready carbon fiber, and are buttery smooth. They're not guaranteed to make you win, but they're guaranteed to prevent any post-race blame-game-ing about your equipment not being up to the task. Heads up though, there's a lot of pressure when the weakest part of your bike is you; are you ready for that?

target_product.title: Shiny Object CO2 Inflator
target_product.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesCarrying a pump everywhere can be a drag. Getting a flat tire while you're out is even worse! You know what's not awful? The Portland Design Works Shiny Object CO2 inflator. With this bad boy, you can leave the pump at home and, if you get a flat, you're just a twist of the cartridge away from rolling again! Plus, the Shiny Object has a built-in valve so you can pop a cartridge on there and not have to worry about accidentally emptying your CO2 (say, "goodbye" to premature evacuation)! Did I mention that it works with presta and schrader valves? Well it does, and that means, no matter what you're riding, popping the Shiny Object in your pocket before you head out could be the difference between riding and walking home! It even comes with a CO2 cartridge, a classy leather sleeve, and it'll take any 16g threaded CO2 cartridges you can find, so grab one and get riding! Your friends will totally be jealous of how shiny it is. PDF Instructions

product_info.title: Nantucket Cruiser Pannier Basket
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. Not satisfied with only basketing-out the front of the bike, they've started weaving these amazing basket panniers that hook directly to your rear rack! Pop it off and take it into the store while you grab your groceries, pop it back on your rack when you're done shopping and cruise home! Woven using the highest quality rattan which weathers nicely over time for an antique look, this isn't your average department store-basket, it's a practical work of art that'll help you and your bike thrive in your city!

product_info.title: Knog Blinder Road Rear Light
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesNow for the tale of the Knog Blinder Road Rear. This rear light has a colossal 70 lumen strobe, with numerous settings for every riding situation. With the Knog’s blindingly bright beam, it will be as if you are standing atop Mount Olympus, shouting with the thunder of a thousand sirens. “See me,” you will scream, “FEAR ME!” And all will see you and watch with awe and pure wonder as you ride to battle your foes. Truly, this is the light of heroes. So grab one, and be epic! Specs 70 lumens in strobe mode (peak) Dimensions: W27mm x H76mm x D52mm Weight: 52g Materials: UV-Resistant, industrial-grade Silicone Rubber Body and Straps. Polycarbonate Housing. PMMA Lens. Anodised Aluminium Heat sink. Anodised Aluminium Fascia and solid Stainless Steel MIMLatch. Rechargeable Lithium Polymer (USB). This saves using about 600 AAA Alkaline batteries during the lights lifetime. Features LEDs: 1 x CREE XPD XB-D LED, 3 x Super bright LEDs Lens: Collimated optics. Visibility: Visible from a distance of min. 1000 metres. Incorporates side Illumination with visibility of 290° Beam Angle (degrees): Wide beam 80°. Narrow beam 22° LiPo Technology with battery protection circuit. USB Rechargeable and extension cord included. Constant current drive technology: Maintains consistent brightness throughout specified run-time. Integrated USB Plug: Designed to be exposed to the elements, the plug is also waterproof and will not be damaged by exposure. Waterproof: 100% Waterproof and Dust Proof. Light Modes: 5 light modes: 1.Steady, 2.Fast, 3.Chaser, 4.Peleton, 5. Eco-Flash. Burn time: lasting up to 3.5 hours in Steady mode, 4 hours in Fast, 5 hours in Chaser, 13 hours in Peloton Mode and 20 hours in Eco-Flash. Charge time: 5 hour charge time Button: New longer button push on (0.75sec) prevents accidental activation of your light. Shortpresses switch modes continuously. Similarly, the light is switched off with a long button push off (0.5sec). Low battery indicator Bike Attachment: Tool-less attachment for standard rear posts measuring 22-32mm. Not suitable for aero post design Testing: The Blinder Road has been tested against the following; Drop tests, corrosion tests, UV tests,Electrical shock and static, vibration and impact, temperature and humidity, cycle testing and CE certification.

product_info.title: Leather Little Lifter
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesThe original bicycle frame handle launched by Walnut Studiolo on Kickstarter. The frame handle (a.k.a. “The Little Lifter”!) is a comfortable, stylish, sturdy, and easy-to-use leather handle for carrying your bicycle, whether it's up the stairs, across the tracks, or onto the metro. Designed for commuters, this minimalist handle makes carrying your bike actually feel easier and lighter by lowering the center of gravity and using your normal muscle groups for lifting and holding your bicycle, same as lifting a grocery bag or carrying a briefcase. Most riders pick up their bike by the top tube, which requires you to bend your elbow at an uncomfortable angle. This causes strain on your elbow and shoulder and makes carrying your bike any distance feel awkward. Because it’s easier to lift a bike with the Frame Handle, you’re more in control when walking up stairs or in a crowded setting. The Frame Handle has two adjustable buckles. One that wraps around the down-tube and one around the seat-tube. It can be mounted above the derailleur and below most water bottle cages. The leather used is USA-tanned leather from American steers in St. Louis, Missouri with hardware sourced from an Ohio leather company.

product_info.title: Siva Juliet
product_info.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix Cycles Our Most Popular Platform We started with the Juliet, our best-selling model of all time for its sleek lines, smooth ride, and no-nonsense speed. A flip-flop hub comes standard so you can ride single-speed or fixed, dual water bottle bosses on the frame let you stay hydrated, and we carry over 100 parts and accessories that’ll fit, so the only limit to customization is your imagination. Don’t Waste Watts The Siva Atom converts your bike’s motion into electricity, so you’re not just the motor, you’re a generator! And thanks to the removable battery, the power you put into the pedals gets harnessed to breathe new life into dying electronics. Never worry about getting to the party with a dead phone again! Siva Juliet will get you wherever you’re going with speed, style, and plenty of juice.

target_product.title: Reynolds 66mm Carbon Tubular Pro Wheel
target_product.description: This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix CyclesReynolds 66mm Carbon Tubular Pro Wheel Excuses are cheap. Losing another race, being late for another date, getting chumped again by the grandma on the mountain bike; they're not the end of the world - and they're a heck of a lot cheaper than these wheels. But maybe that's not good enough for you. Maybe you've gone as far as you want to go on excuses and now you want to see how you'll do with nothing standing in your way. These tubeless Reynolds wheels weigh a combined 3lbs 13oz, are made from race-ready carbon fiber, and are buttery smooth. They're not guaranteed to make you win, but they're guaranteed to prevent any post-race blame-game-ing about your equipment not being up to the task. Heads up though, there's a lot of pressure when the weakest part of your bike is you; are you ready for that?

A flip-flop hub comes standard so you can ride single-speed or fixed, dual water bottle bosses on the frame let you stay hydrated, and we carry over 100 parts and accessories that’ll fit, so the only limit to customization is your imagination. Don’t Waste Watts The Siva Atom converts your bike’s motion into electricity, so you’re not just the motor, you’re a generator! And thanks to the removable battery, the power you put into the pedals gets harnessed to breathe new life into dying electronics. Never worry about getting to the party with a dead phone again! Siva Juliet will get you wherever you’re going with speed, style, and plenty of juice.
